&lt;h1&gt;Getting Started with BigLedger&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your essential first steps with BigLedger&amp;rsquo;s Business Operating System. This section covers everything you need to know to get up and running quickly and efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Quick Start Guide&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="quick-start-guide"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#quick-start-guide" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;New to BigLedger? Follow this path for the fastest onboarding experience:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-cards hx:mt-4 hx:gap-4 hx:grid not-prose" style="--hextra-cards-grid-cols: 3;"&gt;
&lt;a
